{"lang": "zh_TW", "eventid": "act40side", "eventName": "相見歡", "entryType": "ACTIVITY", "storyCode": "OR-3", "avgTag": "行動後", "storyName": "油潑扯麵", "storyInfo": "煌做的長壽麵得到了小大廚的認可。驚蟄在得知還有其他方式能夠轉移學宮檔案後，找到了新的調查方向。\n", "storyList": [{"id": 0, "prop": "HEADER", "attributes": {"key": "title_test", "is_skippable": "true", "fit_mode": "BLACK_MASK"}}, {"id": 1, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 2, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 3, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 4, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "58_g1_yusrestaurant", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 5, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 6, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 7, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "一大早，小飯館的門外尚冷清，僅有幾隻羽獸在落葉上來回跳躍。"}}, {"id": 8, "prop": "playsound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_wing"}}, {"id": 9, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "對門大理寺的值夜人打了個長長的呵欠，驚得羽獸四散飛離。"}}, {"id": 10, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 11, "prop": "playMusic", "attributes": {"key": "$normal_loop", "volume": 0.6}}, {"id": 12, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_2026_yu_1#1$1", "duration": 1.5}}, {"id": 13, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.5}}, {"id": 14, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "啊——嗚……", "name": "小大廚"}, "figure_art": "avg_2026_yu_1#1$1"}, {"id": 15, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_2026_yu_1#19$1"}}, {"id": 16, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "昨晚做了惡夢，夢見有隻循獸把我廚房裡的麵粉都吃光了。好可怕……", "name": "小大廚"}, "figure_art": "avg_2026_yu_1#19$1"}, {"id": 17, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 18, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 19, "prop": "playsound", "attributes": {"key": "$rungeneral", "loop": "true", "channel": "bgs"}}, {"id": 20, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_1040_blaze2_1#1$1", "posfrom": "200,0", "posto": "0,0", "duration": 0.7}}, {"id": 21, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 22, "prop": "StopSound", "attributes": {"channel": "bgs", "fadetime": 0.5}}, {"id": 23, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.3}}, {"id": 24, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "早！", "name": "煌"}, "figure_art": "avg_1040_blaze2_1#1$1"}, {"id": 25, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 26, "prop": "CameraShake", "attributes": {"duration": 0.1, "xstrength": 10.0, "ystrength": 10.0, "vibrato": 10.0, "randomness": 90.0, "fadeout": "true", "block": "false"}}, {"id": 27, "prop": "playsound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_plateplace"}}, {"id": 28, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.5}}, {"id": 29, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_1040_blaze2_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 30, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "請！", "name": "煌"}, "figure_art": "avg_1040_blaze2_1#1$1"}, {"id": 31, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_2026_yu_1#8$1"}}, {"id": 32, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你……學會了？", "name": "小大廚"}, "figure_art": "avg_2026_yu_1#8$1"}, {"id": 33, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_2026_yu_1#9$1"}}, {"id": 34, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你這黑眼圈……難道真做了一整夜？", "name": "小大廚"}, "figure_art": "avg_2026_yu_1#9$1"}, {"id": 35, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_1040_blaze2_1#6$1"}}, {"id": 36, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "哈哈，也就到後半宿吧……行箸到現在還沒醒呢。", "name": "煌"}, "figure_art": "avg_1040_blaze2_1#6$1"}, {"id": 37, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_1040_blaze2_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 38, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "先不說別的了，快嚐嚐這麵！", "name": "煌"}, "figure_art": "avg_1040_blaze2_1#1$1"}, {"id": 39, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_2026_yu_1#9$1"}}, {"id": 40, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你……啊？", "name": "小大廚"}, "figure_art": "avg_2026_yu_1#9$1"}, {"id": 41, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_2026_yu_1#15$1"}}, {"id": 42, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你沒學會和麵，就煮了一把麵線來給我交差？！", "name": "小大廚"}, "figure_art": "avg_2026_yu_1#15$1"}, {"id": 43, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_1040_blaze2_1#2$1"}}, {"id": 44, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這可不是一般的麵線。這是行箸和我挑遍了市面上所有種類的麵線後，精心挑選出的口感最接近你做的麵的一款。", "name": "煌"}, "figure_art": "avg_1040_blaze2_1#2$1"}, {"id": 45, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "當然，相比於手工麵，口感還是略差一些的。不過行箸還對你湯底配方稍微進行了一點調整——保證做出來的口味和你做的差不多。", "name": "煌"}, "figure_art": "avg_1040_blaze2_1#2$1"}, {"id": 46, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_2026_yu_1#15$1"}}, {"id": 47, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "歪門邪說，投機取巧，還亂改我的配方！", "name": "小大廚"}, "figure_art": "avg_2026_yu_1#15$1"}, {"id": 48, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_1040_blaze2_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 49, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "先別急著下結論，你嚐嚐再說嘛！", "name": "煌"}, "figure_art": "avg_1040_blaze2_1#1$1"}, {"id": 50, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 51, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_2026_yu_1#15$1", "focus": "n"}}, {"id": 52, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "小大廚皺著眉，用筷子挑起幾縷麵，小心翼翼地聞了聞，才送入口中。"}}, {"id": 53, "prop": "playsound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_eatnoodle_single", "volume": 0.5}}, {"id": 54, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_2026_yu_1#15$1"}}, {"id": 55, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……唔。", "name": "小大廚"}, "figure_art": "avg_2026_yu_1#15$1"}, {"id": 56, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_1040_blaze2_1#2$1"}}, {"id": 57, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "怎麼樣？", "name": "煌"}, "figure_art": "avg_1040_blaze2_1#2$1"}, {"id": 58, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_2026_yu_1#9$1"}}, {"id": 59, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……嗯。", "name": "小大廚"}, "figure_art": "avg_2026_yu_1#9$1"}, {"id": 60, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_1040_blaze2_1#2$1"}}, {"id": 61, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "說話啊！", "name": "煌"}, "figure_art": "avg_1040_blaze2_1#2$1"}, {"id": 62, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_2026_yu_1#8$1"}}, {"id": 63, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你們……為什麼會覺得這樣做就可以？", "name": "小大廚"}, "figure_art": "avg_2026_yu_1#8$1"}, {"id": 64, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_1040_blaze2_1#4$1"}}, {"id": 65, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "主要是行箸都快餓得不行了。當時想著，與其就這麼和麵糰乾耗著，不如先用你的配方做碗我能做的麵給她吃。", "name": "煌"}, "figure_art": "avg_1040_blaze2_1#4$1"}, {"id": 66, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "後來想了想，長壽麵最重要的可能不是味道，而是讓吃麵的人有被祝福的感覺。", "name": "煌"}, "figure_art": "avg_1040_blaze2_1#4$1"}, {"id": 67, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_1040_blaze2_1#2$1"}}, {"id": 68, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "有些人就是學不會你這一手做麵條的功夫，但是用一把麵線也能為自己或家人送上祝福，這就是長壽麵的意義。", "name": "煌"}, "figure_art": "avg_1040_blaze2_1#2$1"}, {"id": 69, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_1040_blaze2_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 70, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你看，這麵條金黃油亮，是不是比你那一碗看起來還熱鬧一點？", "name": "煌"}, "figure_art": "avg_1040_blaze2_1#1$1"}, {"id": 71, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_1040_blaze2_1#7$1"}}, {"id": 72, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "呃……當然，投機取巧也是事實啦……", "name": "煌"}, "figure_art": "avg_1040_blaze2_1#7$1"}, {"id": 73, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_2026_yu_1#9$1"}}, {"id": 74, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你說“被祝福的感覺”……你覺得自己做出來了嗎？", "name": "小大廚"}, "figure_art": "avg_2026_yu_1#9$1"}, {"id": 75, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_1040_blaze2_1#2$1"}}, {"id": 76, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我……應該吧？", "name": "煌"}, "figure_art": "avg_1040_blaze2_1#2$1"}, {"id": 77, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_1040_blaze2_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 78, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "昨晚第一次成功做出這碗麵的時候，我和行箸一起分享了。我覺得吃得很開心，她還偷偷擦眼淚來著……", "name": "煌"}, "figure_art": "avg_1040_blaze2_1#1$1"}, {"id": 79, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_2026_yu_1#4$1"}}, {"id": 80, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "把手工麵換成了麵線，也跟著調整了香油和鹽的用量，倒也算動了腦子……那位姑娘的舌頭真是厲害。", "name": "小大廚"}, "figure_art": "avg_2026_yu_1#4$1"}, {"id": 81, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_2026_yu_1#2$1"}}, {"id": 82, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "但是麵線煮完需要過涼水，你做是做了，卻沒把涼水瀝乾。", "name": "小大廚"}, "figure_art": "avg_2026_yu_1#2$1"}, {"id": 83, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "涼水留得太多，降低了湯的溫度，也影響了整碗麵的口感。要想精益求精的話，這些細節下次最好也要照顧到。", "name": "小大廚"}, "figure_art": "avg_2026_yu_1#2$1"}, {"id": 84, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_1040_blaze2_1#5$1"}}, {"id": 85, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "啊……好，我記住了！", "name": "煌"}, "figure_art": "avg_1040_blaze2_1#5$1"}, {"id": 86, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_1040_blaze2_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 87, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "欸，你說這話的意思是……", "name": "煌"}, "figure_art": "avg_1040_blaze2_1#1$1"}, {"id": 88, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_2026_yu_1#3$1"}}, {"id": 89, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "打住，我就是看在你花了心思的分上，決定繼續教你罷了。", "name": "小大廚"}, "figure_art": "avg_2026_yu_1#3$1"}, {"id": 90, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_2026_yu_1#2$1"}}, {"id": 91, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "和麵還是要接著練的，你總不能真的打算帶著一把麵線去參加比賽吧？", "name": "小大廚"}, "figure_art": "avg_2026_yu_1#2$1"}, {"id": 92, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_1040_blaze2_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 93, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "嘿嘿，好！", "name": "煌"}, "figure_art": "avg_1040_blaze2_1#1$1"}, {"id": 94, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_2026_yu_1#2$1"}}, {"id": 95, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這只是師父心軟，覺得徒弟開竅了一點。但客人到底買不買單，還是要考驗一番的。", "name": "小大廚"}, "figure_art": "avg_2026_yu_1#2$1"}, {"id": 96, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_1040_blaze2_1#2$1"}}, {"id": 97, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這……要怎麼考驗？", "name": "煌"}, "figure_art": "avg_1040_blaze2_1#2$1"}, {"id": 98, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_2026_yu_1#2$1"}}, {"id": 99, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "等會客人來了，如果有點麵條的，你就做一碗送去。", "name": "小大廚"}, "figure_art": "avg_2026_yu_1#2$1"}, {"id": 100, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "客人要是覺得不好吃，那你就接著練習吧。", "name": "小大廚"}, "figure_art": "avg_2026_yu_1#2$1"}, {"id": 101, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_1040_blaze2_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 102, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……我這就去！", "name": "煌"}, "figure_art": "avg_1040_blaze2_1#1$1"}, {"id": 103, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 104, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 105, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 106, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "58_g1_yusrestaurant", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 107, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 108, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$dooropenquite"}}, {"id": 109, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 110, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_walkfast"}}, {"id": 111, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_1040_blaze2_1#1$1", "duration": 0.5}}, {"id": 112, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 113, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這位客人！要不要來一碗本店新推出的特色長壽麵！", "name": "煌"}, "figure_art": "avg_1040_blaze2_1#1$1"}, {"id": 114, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 115, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "今天又不是我的生日，怎麼平白無故讓我吃長壽麵？", "name": "衣著光鮮的食客"}, "figure_art": "avg_1040_blaze2_1#1$1"}, {"id": 116, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_1040_blaze2_1#5$1"}}, {"id": 117, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "呃……小店新菜品試吃，讓客人免費品嚐！", "name": "煌"}, "figure_art": "avg_1040_blaze2_1#5$1"}, {"id": 118, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_1040_blaze2_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 119, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不對……您要是吃完覺得滿意，還是付一下錢比較好，我也得向我們老闆交差……", "name": "煌"}, "figure_art": "avg_1040_blaze2_1#1$1"}, {"id": 120, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 121, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "真有趣，這小店的生意還有這種做法。", "name": "衣著光鮮的食客"}, "figure_art": "avg_1040_blaze2_1#1$1"}, {"id": 122, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "把麵放下吧，就算我點的。", "name": "衣著光鮮的食客"}, "figure_art": "avg_1040_blaze2_1#1$1"}, {"id": 123, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_1040_blaze2_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 124, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "（熱切的眼神）", "name": "煌"}, "figure_art": "avg_1040_blaze2_1#1$1"}, {"id": 125, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 126, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "呃……還有事嗎？", "name": "衣著光鮮的食客"}, "figure_art": "avg_1040_blaze2_1#1$1"}, {"id": 127, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_1040_blaze2_1#5$1"}}, {"id": 128, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "沒，沒！我就是想等您吃過後，聽聽您的評價。", "name": "煌"}, "figure_art": "avg_1040_blaze2_1#5$1"}, {"id": 129, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 130, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "好好……我吃就是。", "name": "衣著光鮮的食客"}, "figure_art": "avg_1040_blaze2_1#5$1"}, {"id": 131, "prop": "playsound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_dishes"}}, {"id": 132, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "食客拿起筷子，先後夾起一根麵、一片青菜、一點蔥花，都仔細品嚐過。"}}, {"id": 133, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "他動作優雅，可不一會的工夫，一碗麵已經見底。"}}, {"id": 134, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_1040_blaze2_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 135, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "味道如何？", "name": "煌"}, "figure_art": "avg_1040_blaze2_1#1$1"}, {"id": 136, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 137, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "嗯……好吃，很好吃。", "name": "衣著光鮮的食客"}, "figure_art": "avg_1040_blaze2_1#1$1"}, {"id": 138, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_1040_blaze2_1#11$1"}}, {"id": 139, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "真……真的？！", "name": "煌"}, "figure_art": "avg_1040_blaze2_1#11$1"}, {"id": 140, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 141, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這湯很鮮，所用食材也很講究，如果再燉上一天一夜，味道能更完美。", "name": "衣著光鮮的食客"}, "figure_art": "avg_1040_blaze2_1#11$1"}, {"id": 142, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "可是我已經很餓了，等不了那麼久。如果為了那點“完美”再等上一天一夜，我恐怕早就餓死了。", "name": "衣著光鮮的食客"}, "figure_art": "avg_1040_blaze2_1#11$1"}, {"id": 143, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "他想要求一份完美的味道，但客人卻等不住了。", "name": "衣著光鮮的食客"}, "figure_art": "avg_1040_blaze2_1#11$1"}, {"id": 144, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "即便我願意等他，有些事也是沒辦法再等下去了。", "name": "衣著光鮮的食客"}, "figure_art": "avg_1040_blaze2_1#11$1"}, {"id": 145, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_1040_blaze2_1#2$1"}}, {"id": 146, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "您這話……", "name": "煌"}, "figure_art": "avg_1040_blaze2_1#2$1"}, {"id": 147, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 148, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不要緊，你把我的話轉告你們老闆就好。", "name": "衣著光鮮的食客"}, "figure_art": "avg_1040_blaze2_1#2$1"}, {"id": 149, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "食客站起身，他衣服上的紋樣流光溢彩，光線在他身側扭曲虛化，讓人看不清他的面孔。"}}, {"id": 150, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_1040_blaze2_1#8$1"}}, {"id": 151, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "欸，您……您還沒給錢呢！", "name": "煌"}, "figure_art": "avg_1040_blaze2_1#8$1"}, {"id": 152, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 153, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 154, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1236_1#9$1", "duration": 1.0}}, {"id": 155, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.5}}, {"id": 156, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "從我帳上扣吧。", "name": "衣著光鮮的食客"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1236_1#9$1"}, {"id": 157, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {"fadetime": 2.0}}, {"id": 158, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 159, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 160, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 161, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 162, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "58_g8_baizaoacademy", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 163, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 164, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 165, "prop": "playMusic", "attributes": {"intro": "$mist_intro", "key": "$mist_loop", "volume": 0.6}}, {"id": 166, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "left", "name": "avg_npc_1644_1#1$1", "duration": 1.0}}, {"id": 167, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "right", "name": "avg_npc_1620_1#1$1", "duration": 1.0}}, {"id": 168, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 169, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "right", "name": "avg_npc_1620_1#1$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 170, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不管你要查的到底是什麼，出去以後，千萬不要說這份檔案資料是從學宮拿到的，記住了？", "name": "景教授"}}, {"id": 171, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "left", "name": "avg_npc_1644_1#1$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 172, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "明白……", "name": "麟青硯"}}, {"id": 173, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "right", "name": "avg_npc_1620_1#8$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 174, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "怎麼了？還有什麼問題嗎？", "name": "景教授"}}, {"id": 175, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "left", "name": "avg_npc_1644_1#2$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 176, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你還記不記得……1062年，那場血案……", "name": "麟青硯"}}, {"id": 177, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "right", "name": "avg_npc_1620_1#2$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 178, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……這可不是什麼能隨便談起的話題。", "name": "景教授"}}, {"id": 179, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "left", "name": "avg_npc_1644_1#3$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 180, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……我只是突然想起……", "name": "麟青硯"}}, {"id": 181, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你口中那位，支持學界變法改革，造福無數寒門學子的太師，和四十年前，弒君謀逆的太師，真的是同一個人嗎……", "name": "麟青硯"}}, {"id": 182, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "right", "name": "avg_npc_1620_1#1$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 183, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……我沒有辦法回答你的問題。不瞭解的事，我絕不會妄言。", "name": "景教授"}}, {"id": 184, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "right", "name": "avg_npc_1620_1#3$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 185, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我沒有見過那位太師，只是曾經讀過她一些關於民生政治的論著。從書中能看出作者的見識之深、學識之廣，這也讓我獲益良多。", "name": "景教授"}}, {"id": 186, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "但恐怕，人是很難一概而論的。", "name": "景教授"}}, {"id": 187, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "left", "name": "avg_npc_1644_1#13$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 188, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你這樣說，不正意味著，你對於當年案件的結果，並不是完全相信的嗎？", "name": "麟青硯"}}, {"id": 189, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "right", "name": "avg_npc_1620_1#8$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 190, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "青硯，你臉上可從來藏不住事。", "name": "景教授"}}, {"id": 191, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你果然還是……", "name": "景教授"}}, {"id": 192, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "left", "name": "avg_npc_1644_1#1$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 193, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "大理寺的卷宗，容不下不清不白的案件……不管是多大的案件。", "name": "麟青硯"}}, {"id": 194, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這是大理寺少卿的職責。", "name": "麟青硯"}}, {"id": 195, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "right", "name": "avg_npc_1620_1#1$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 196, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你要做的事，我不會勸你別做。可無論如何，你都要學會保護好自己。", "name": "景教授"}}, {"id": 197, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "唉……你的父母入山閉關前還拜託我對你多加關照，你要是出了什麼事，我可就沒臉再去見他們了。", "name": "景教授"}}, {"id": 198, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "left", "name": "avg_npc_1644_1#11$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 199, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我又不是小輩，怎麼會總要人照顧——", "name": "麟青硯"}}, {"id": 200, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "right", "name": "avg_npc_1620_1#1$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 201, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "年輕的時候，任誰都是這樣的想法。可作為母親，看著左樂一天天長大，我心裡也壓上了一塊石頭。", "name": "景教授"}}, {"id": 202, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "當長輩的不惦記著孩子的安危，又能惦記些什麼呢？", "name": "景教授"}}, {"id": 203, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "可如果要讓他們知道，我為了你的“安危”考慮，阻止你履行大理寺少卿的職責，他們才會真的怪我吧。", "name": "景教授"}}, {"id": 204, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "left", "name": "avg_npc_1644_1#9$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 205, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "多謝……姐姐……", "name": "麟青硯"}}, {"id": 206, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "right", "name": "avg_npc_1620_1#9$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 207, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "唉……你口口聲聲叫我姐姐，可在我眼裡，你一直都是和左樂一輩的孩子。", "name": "景教授"}}, {"id": 208, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "left", "name": "avg_npc_1644_1#1$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 209, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "說起來，玉門已經接近百灶，這幾天，你還沒有見過左將軍？", "name": "麟青硯"}}, {"id": 210, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "right", "name": "avg_npc_1620_1#1$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 211, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "局勢已經迫在眉睫。兵部日夜開會研究，他也必須坐鎮一線。", "name": "景教授"}}, {"id": 212, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我和他，誰都不能擅離職守。", "name": "景教授"}}, {"id": 213, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "left", "name": "avg_npc_1644_1#11$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 214, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……", "name": "麟青硯"}}, {"id": 215, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這場爭端……難道真的無法避免了嗎？", "name": "麟青硯"}}, {"id": 216, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "right", "name": "avg_npc_1620_1#1$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 217, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這不是我可以決斷的事。", "name": "景教授"}}, {"id": 218, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "作為兵部參知，我的職責就是盡最大的努力，盡可能精準地演算戰爭結果。要是心存偏私，那就是對大炎萬千百姓的不負責。", "name": "景教授"}}, {"id": 219, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你不會在你的職責中退讓分毫，那我也一樣。", "name": "景教授"}}, {"id": 220, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "left", "name": "avg_npc_1644_1#3$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 221, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "希望一切，平安順遂……", "name": "麟青硯"}}, {"id": 222, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "right", "name": "avg_npc_1620_1#9$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 223, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "倒也不用太過擔心，如果是無可避免的結果，那不如泰然處之。", "name": "景教授"}}, {"id": 224, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "中秋節的時候，要是自己一個人的話，就來家裡吃頓飯吧。", "name": "景教授"}}, {"id": 225, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "left", "name": "avg_npc_1644_1#14$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 226, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "嗯，一定……", "name": "麟青硯"}}, {"id": 227, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "right", "name": "avg_npc_1620_1#8$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 228, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "等等……我突然想起來。", "name": "景教授"}}, {"id": 229, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你剛才不是問我，誰可以修改學宮的檔案資料？", "name": "景教授"}}, {"id": 230, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "right", "name": "avg_npc_1620_1#3$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 231, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "雖然是極端情況，但也的確有過這樣的個例……", "name": "景教授"}}, {"id": 232, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "left", "name": "avg_npc_1644_1#13$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 233, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你是說……", "name": "麟青硯"}}, {"id": 234, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "right", "name": "avg_npc_1620_1#1$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 235, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不，不能說是修改。但如果學宮裡的某一份檔案資料完全消失不見的話，那只能是轉移去了一個地方——", "name": "景教授"}}, {"id": 236, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "right", "name": "avg_npc_1620_1#5$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 237, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……刑部死獄。", "name": "景教授"}}, {"id": 238, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 239, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 240, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 241, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 242, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "35_g7_zuosroom", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 243, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 244, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 245, "prop": "playsound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_gen_walk_n"}}, {"id": 246, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4121_zuole_1#1$1", "duration": 1.0}}, {"id": 247, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 248, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……", "name": "左樂"}, "figure_art": "avg_4121_zuole_1#1$1"}, {"id": 249, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "父親不在……？", "name": "左樂"}, "figure_art": "avg_4121_zuole_1#1$1"}, {"id": 250, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 251, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "距上次來到這裡轉眼已過了大半年的時間，屋中陳設未變，只有沙盤上，象徵戰火的標誌又多出不少。"}}, {"id": 252, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "孤城拒守，兩相遙望。"}}, {"id": 253, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "公子……", "name": "？？？"}, "figure_art": "avg_4121_zuole_1#1$1"}, {"id": 254, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "熟悉而厚重的聲音在身後響起。"}}, {"id": 255, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 256, "prop": "playsound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_gen_walk_n"}}, {"id": 257, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_299_1#1$1", "duration": 1.5}}, {"id": 258, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.5}}, {"id": 259, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4121_zuole_1#6$1"}}, {"id": 260, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "太合叔！", "name": "左樂"}, "figure_art": "avg_4121_zuole_1#6$1"}, {"id": 261, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4121_zuole_1#10$1"}}, {"id": 262, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你……你的傷？", "name": "左樂"}, "figure_art": "avg_4121_zuole_1#10$1"}, {"id": 263, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_299_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 264, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "半個月前才勉強可以行動，總算不用整日臥床了。", "name": "太合"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_299_1#1$1"}, {"id": 265, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "focus": "n"}}, {"id": 266, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "左樂怔怔地看著眼前那已幾乎不是自己記憶中容貌的太合。"}}, {"id": 267, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "風掀起了他斗篷的一角，左樂看到了那寬大衣袍下枯瘦的身形。"}}, {"id": 268, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "曾經那個鐵打般的漢子，如今卻是形銷骨立，彷彿經不住城頭的一陣風。"}}, {"id": 269, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4121_zuole_1#7$1"}}, {"id": 270, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "太合叔……", "name": "左樂"}, "figure_art": "avg_4121_zuole_1#7$1"}, {"id": 271, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_299_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 272, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這身拳腳功夫不過是外物，我依然是肅政院的監察御史，心中抱負總有施展之處。", "name": "太合"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_299_1#1$1"}, {"id": 273, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "公子若是還要這樣掛懷，那就是看輕太合了。", "name": "太合"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_299_1#1$1"}, {"id": 274, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4121_zuole_1#6$1"}}, {"id": 275, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不……怎會……", "name": "左樂"}, "figure_art": "avg_4121_zuole_1#6$1"}, {"id": 276, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4121_zuole_1#8$1"}}, {"id": 277, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "太合叔一身才學，怎會被這區區傷病限制住！", "name": "左樂"}, "figure_art": "avg_4121_zuole_1#8$1"}, {"id": 278, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_299_1#6$1"}}, {"id": 279, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……", "name": "太合"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_299_1#6$1"}, {"id": 280, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "倒是公子，大半年未見，看上去更壯實了些。將軍見到你，應當欣慰。", "name": "太合"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_299_1#6$1"}, {"id": 281, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4121_zuole_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 282, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "對了，父親他……？", "name": "左樂"}, "figure_art": "avg_4121_zuole_1#1$1"}, {"id": 283, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_299_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 284, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "將軍這幾天一直在與司歲台和兵部開會議事，幾乎沒有片刻閒暇。", "name": "太合"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_299_1#1$1"}, {"id": 285, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4121_zuole_1#10$1"}}, {"id": 286, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "現在的局勢……", "name": "左樂"}, "figure_art": "avg_4121_zuole_1#10$1"}, {"id": 287, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_299_1#2$1"}}, {"id": 288, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "只在旦夕。", "name": "太合"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_299_1#2$1"}, {"id": 289, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4121_zuole_1#10$1"}}, {"id": 290, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……現在朝中的態度，是不惜一戰嗎？", "name": "左樂"}, "figure_art": "avg_4121_zuole_1#10$1"}, {"id": 291, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_299_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 292, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "大荒城變故發生後，歲獸一事已然不是司歲台所能控制。", "name": "太合"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_299_1#1$1"}, {"id": 293, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "朝中內閣、六部，雖然還有些爭議，但態度已經明確——", "name": "太合"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_299_1#1$1"}, {"id": 294, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_299_1#2$1"}}, {"id": 295, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "永絕後患。", "name": "太合"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_299_1#2$1"}, {"id": 296, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4121_zuole_1#7$1"}}, {"id": 297, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "可是，這一戰的後果……", "name": "左樂"}, "figure_art": "avg_4121_zuole_1#7$1"}, {"id": 298, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 299, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 300, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 301, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 302, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_2025_shu_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 303, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "35_mini01_villagevacancy", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 304, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 305, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 306, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 307, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 308, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 309, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 310, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_2024_chyue_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 311, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "35_g5_swordcastingworkshop", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 312, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 313, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 314, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 315, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 316, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 317, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 318, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_2023_ling_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 319, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "25_g07_fairyland_1", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 320, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 321, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 322, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 323, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 324, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 325, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 326, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avgnew_2014_nian_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 327, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avgnew_2015_dusk_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 328, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "25_g08_pavilion", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 329, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 330, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 331, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 332, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.5, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 333, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 334, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4121_zuole_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 335, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "35_g7_zuosroom", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 336, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.5, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 337, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.5}}, {"id": 338, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我聽說，月前，有其他秉燭人在百灶附近發現了那罪人的蹤跡。", "name": "左樂"}, "figure_art": "avg_4121_zuole_1#1$1"}, {"id": 339, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_299_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 340, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "是的……我也聽說了此事。", "name": "太合"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_299_1#1$1"}, {"id": 341, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "朝廷已經嚴加防備，出動了多位禁軍。", "name": "太合"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_299_1#1$1"}, {"id": 342, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4121_zuole_1#10$1"}}, {"id": 343, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "竟然連禁軍都……", "name": "左樂"}, "figure_art": "avg_4121_zuole_1#10$1"}, {"id": 344, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_299_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 345, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "那罪人的手段難以預料，是當下最緊要的威脅。", "name": "太合"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_299_1#1$1"}, {"id": 346, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4121_zuole_1#3$1"}}, {"id": 347, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我有一個猜想，或許……", "name": "左樂"}, "figure_art": "avg_4121_zuole_1#3$1"}, {"id": 348, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4121_zuole_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 349, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "現在百灶城中，還有一位代理人……", "name": "左樂"}, "figure_art": "avg_4121_zuole_1#1$1"}, {"id": 350, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這一位“年紀”最小的代理人，也是最為特殊的一位。", "name": "左樂"}, "figure_art": "avg_4121_zuole_1#1$1"}, {"id": 351, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "據司歲台的觀測，他從走出那座陵墓起，這數百年裡從未施展過任何權能。司歲台也不知該對他如何是好……", "name": "左樂"}, "figure_art": "avg_4121_zuole_1#1$1"}, {"id": 352, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4121_zuole_1#4$1"}}, {"id": 353, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "唯有一事可疑——百年前，他在望越獄後來到百灶，之後便一直逗留此處。", "name": "左樂"}, "figure_art": "avg_4121_zuole_1#4$1"}, {"id": 354, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "望之前曾頻繁地接觸其他代理人，他這次回來，恐怕留在百灶的這一位，也在他的計劃之內。", "name": "左樂"}, "figure_art": "avg_4121_zuole_1#4$1"}, {"id": 355, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_299_1#4$1"}}, {"id": 356, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "公子有何打算？", "name": "太合"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_299_1#4$1"}, {"id": 357, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4121_zuole_1#2$1"}}, {"id": 358, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我不知道……所以要先去看個明白。", "name": "左樂"}, "figure_art": "avg_4121_zuole_1#2$1"}, {"id": 359, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4121_zuole_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 360, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我自己去看。", "name": "左樂"}, "figure_art": "avg_4121_zuole_1#1$1"}, {"id": 361, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {"fadetime": 2.0}}, {"id": 362, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 363, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 364, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 365, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 366, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "58_g13_yuskitchen", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 367, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 368, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 369, "prop": "playMusic", "attributes": {"intro": "$sjoyasorrow_intro", "key": "$sjoyasorrow_loop", "volume": 0.6}}, {"id": 370, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_1040_blaze2_1#1$1", "duration": 0.5}}, {"id": 371, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 372, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "呼……完成！", "name": "煌"}, "figure_art": "avg_1040_blaze2_1#1$1"}, {"id": 373, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_1040_blaze2_1#7$1"}}, {"id": 374, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "怎麼樣？從洗菜開始的每一道工序，我已經記得滾瓜爛熟了！一點都不用人幫忙！", "name": "煌"}, "figure_art": "avg_1040_blaze2_1#7$1"}, {"id": 375, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_1040_blaze2_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 376, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "也多虧行箸幫我想的辦法，只要在上手和麵之前，先把手放在冰水裡泡上五分鐘就沒有問題了！", "name": "煌"}, "figure_art": "avg_1040_blaze2_1#1$1"}, {"id": 377, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4172_xingzh_1#11$1"}}, {"id": 378, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "嗯……看起來成色不錯，味道上也有些神似小大廚的手藝了。", "name": "行箸"}, "figure_art": "avg_4172_xingzh_1#11$1"}, {"id": 379, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_2026_yu_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 380, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "勉勉強強吧，還遠談不上以假亂真呢。", "name": "小大廚"}, "figure_art": "avg_2026_yu_1#1$1"}, {"id": 381, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "要是我這麼多年的手藝，被一個沒下過廚的人隨隨便便就學會了，那我不是白混了。", "name": "小大廚"}, "figure_art": "avg_2026_yu_1#1$1"}, {"id": 382, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_1040_blaze2_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 383, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "努力了這麼多天，明天就要比賽了，你就不能說點鼓勵的話……", "name": "煌"}, "figure_art": "avg_1040_blaze2_1#1$1"}, {"id": 384, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_2026_yu_1#15$1"}}, {"id": 385, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我是怕你得意忘形……不過留點心氣也好，別到時候見了莫不服被嚇得連菜刀都不會用了。", "name": "小大廚"}, "figure_art": "avg_2026_yu_1#15$1"}, {"id": 386, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_2026_yu_1#21$1"}}, {"id": 387, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "沒什麼好怕的，莫不服倚老賣老，你就去給他一點年輕人的顏色看看。", "name": "小大廚"}, "figure_art": "avg_2026_yu_1#21$1"}, {"id": 388, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_1040_blaze2_1#5$1"}}, {"id": 389, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "好！", "name": "煌"}, "figure_art": "avg_1040_blaze2_1#5$1"}, {"id": 390, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "萬事俱備，明天就去決戰鼎豐樓。", "name": "煌"}, "figure_art": "avg_1040_blaze2_1#5$1"}, {"id": 391, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 392, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 393, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 394, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {"fadetime": 2.0}}, {"id": 395, "prop": "Image", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 396, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 397, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": ""}}], "OPTIONTRACE": true}